Description:
On the way you meet two young men, the shorter one says to you:

"Hello, we are alchemists specialising in transmutations. We're a bit short of magic shards, so for 200 shards we can increase one of your physical abilities, 1000 shards if it's for all four of you.

In this type of transmutation the principle of equivalent exchange applies, so if you want to gain something you have to sacrifice something in return.
DescriptionAction: Today you can gain 2 speed in exchange for 15 max hp."
